inputFormat: The first line contains a single integer $ n $ $ (1<=n<=5·10^{5}) $ . The next line contains $ n $ integers $ a_{1},a_{2},...,a_{n} $ $ (1<=a_{i}<=10^{9}) $ .
outputFormat:
In the first line print a single integer $ 4m $ — the maximal possible length of required sequence $ b $ . In the second line print $ 4m $ integers $ b_{1},b_{2},...,b_{4m} $ , that is required sequence.

If there are multiple optimal answers you may print any of them.
translation: 给出一个序列 $\{a_i\}$，要求出其一个最长的子序列 $\{b_i\}$，使得这个子序列的长度 $len$ 满足 $len=4m$ （$m \in N^*$），且对于任意的 $k\in[0,m),k\in N^*$，都有 $b_{4k+1}=b_{4k+3}$ ，$b_{4k+2}=b_{4k+4}$ 成立。
